e%20cow%20in%20good%20condition%20there%E2%80%A6There%20were%20no%20calves%20in%20the%20gaushala%2C%20which%20means%20all%20of%20them%20were%20sold%20off.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EISKCON%2C%20in%20its%20statement%2C%20said%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20pained%20by%20these%20defamatory%2C%20slanderous%2C%20and%20malicious%20accusations%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20leave%20any%20stone%20unturned%20in%20our%20pursuit%20of%20justice%20against%20the%20fallacious%20propaganda%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20defence%2C%20ISKCON%20said%20that%20it%20has%20pioneered%20cow%20protection%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20where%20beef%20is%20a%20staple%20diet.%20%E2%80%9CWithin%20India%2C%20ISKCON%20runs%20more%20than%2060%20goshalas%20protecting%20hundreds%20of%20sacred%20cows%20and%20bulls%20and%20providing%20personalised%20care%20for%20their%20entire%20lifetime.%20Many%20of%20the%20cows%20presently%20served%20in%20ISKCON%E2%80%99s%20goshalas%20were%20brought%20to%20us%20after%20being%20found%20abandoned%2C%20injured%2C%20or%20rescued%20from%20being%20slaughtered%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20religious%20organisation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fiskcon-sells-cows-to-butchers-claims-bjp-mp-maneka-gandhi%2Farticle67354933.ece%5C%22%3Eexplained%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20huge%20following%20across%20the%20world%2C%20ISKCON%20is%20a%20well-known%20Hindu%20religious%20and%20spiritual%20order.%20It%20was%20established%20by%20Srila%20Prabhupada%20in%201966%2C%20and%20is%20headquartered%20at%20Mayapur%20in%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Nadia%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696064636000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fmaneka-gandhi-story_647_030717102741.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmaneka-gandhi-gets-rs-100-crore-defamation-notice-for-calling-iskcon-biggest-cheat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'ISKCON%20establishes%20ga