2US%20Congress%20House%20Session%20starts%20with%20Sikh%20prayer%20for%20first%20time%20in%20history%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696061219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104063434%2Cimgsize-20636.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-congress-house-session-starts-with-sikh-prayer-for-first-time-in-history%2Farticleshow%2F104061913.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-congress-house-session-starts-with-sikh-prayer-for-first-time-in-history%2Farticleshow%2F104061913.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22If%20Rishi%20Sunak%20Loses%20Election%2C%20Here's%20Who%20Could%20Take%20Over%20UK%20PM%20Post%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERishi%20Sunak%20heads%20to%20the%20Conservative%20Party's%20conference%20this%20weekend%20with%20one%20aim%3A%20convincing%20Britain%20he%20can%20win%20the%20UK's%20next%20general%20election.%20Many%20of%20his%20own%20lawmakers%20are%20already%20preparing%20for%20a%20scenario%20in%20which%20he%20doesn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20has%20spent%20recent%20weeks%20trying%20to%20shore%20up%20his%20base.%20He's%20rowed%20back%20on%20green%20measures%20in%20the%20name%20of%20reducing%20costs%20for%20ordinary%20Britons%20and%20mulled%20a%20reassessment%20of%20the%20HS2%20high-speed%20rail%20link%2C%20the%20UK's%20flagship%20infrastructure%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20national%20polls%20suggest%20he%20won't%20be%20Britain's%20leader%20after%20an%20election%20that%20must%20be%20called%20by%20January%202025.%20The%20Labour%20Party%20has%20enjoyed%20a%20double-digit%20polling%20lead%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%20After%20a%20couple%20of%20recent%20polls%20appeared%20to%20show%20Sunak%20clawing%20back%20ground%2C%20YouGov%20this%20week%20gave%20Labour%20a%2021-point%20advantage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fp629nbt8_labour-conservative-graph_625x300_30_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sunak%2C%2043%2C%20appears%20to%20have%20suppressed%20for%20now%20the%20threat%20of%20an%20internal%20challenge%2C%20many%20Tories%20are%20working%20behind%20the%20scenes%20for%20a%20leadership%20run%20if%20the%20election%20goes%20badly%2C%20according%20to%20interviews%20with%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20Conservative%20lawmakers%2C%20advisers%20and%20donors.%20There%20are%20at%20least%2013%20would-be%20contenders%20to%20watch%20out%20for%2C%20said%20the%20people%2C%20who%20spoke%20to%20Bloomberg%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20said%20the%20subplot%20of%20Tory%20conference%20%E2%80%94%20told%20in%20unsubtle%20speeches%2C%20fringe%20events%20and%20drinks%20at%20hotel%20bars%20%E2%80%94%20was%20the%20battle%20for%20the%20future%20of%20the%20party.%20Another%20told%20Bloomberg%20that%20Sunak%20was%20already%20a%20lame%20duck.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunak's%20backers%20say%20his%20team%20is%20focused%20on%20making%20a%20success%20of%20his%20premiership%20and%20not%20getting%20distracted%20by%20events%20beyond%20their%20control.%20Allies%20of%20all%20the%20possible%20leadership%20hopefuls%20said%20they%20were%20working%20to%20support%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20pushing%20for%20a%20Tory%20election%20win.%20Some%20Tories%20think%20Sunak%20could%20still%20pull%20off%20victory%20or%20stay%20on%20if%20Labour%20fail%20to%20secure%20an%20outright%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20replaces%20Rishi%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20defeat%20is%20going%20to%20depend%20in%20no%20small%20part%20on%20just%20how%20bad%20that%20defeat%20turns%20ou