nkar%2Fstatus%2F1707745474416124227%5C%22%3Espeaking%20at%20Hudson%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20think%20tank%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20September%2029%2C%20on%20the%20topic%20of%20%E2%80%98India%E2%80%99s%20Role%20in%20a%20New%20Pacific%20Order%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20stating%20that%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20aim%20is%20to%20be%20reformist%20rather%20than%20revisionist%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20India%20has%20played%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20%E2%80%9Creforming%E2%80%9D%20the%20World%20Bank%20to%20enable%20it%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20climate%20change%20challenge%20and%20to%20achieve%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs).%20He%20said%20India%E2%80%99s%20role%20would%20be%20to%20make%20global%20institutions%20%E2%80%9Cfit-for-purpose%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20globalisation%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20tremendous%20benefits.%20Nobody%20doubts.%20But%20this%20particular%20model%20of%20globalisation%20has%20evolved%20over%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20Obviously%2C%20it%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20risks%20inherent%2C%20and%20today%20how%20to%20address%20those%20risks%20and%20create%20a%20safer%20world%20is%20part%20of%20the%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Jaishankar%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20presence%20and%20activities%20have%20gone%20up%20significantly%20on%20the%20east%2C%20%E2%80%9Cinto%20the%20Pacific%20and%20beyond%E2%80%9D.%20That%20India%20is%20contributing%20more%20to%20a%20Pacific%20order%2C%20he%20said%2C%20reflects%20the%20rebalancing%20that%20is%20currently%20underway.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20rebalancing%20in%20which%20the%20changed%20capabilities%2C%20positioning%2C%20and%20attitudes%20of%20the%20United%20States%20is%20the%20central%20driving%20factor%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20also%20one%20in%20which%20the%20rise%20of%20China%20and%20its%20implications%20is%20obviously%20a%20very%2C%20very%20crucial%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20question%20of%20the%20India-US%20relationship%2C%20he%20said%20while%20both%20of%20them%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cdealing%E2%80%9D%20with%20each%20other%20for%20decades%2C%20it%20is%20only%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20that%20they%20have%20been%20truly%20%E2%80%9Cworking%E2%80%9D%20with%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20India-Canada%20diplomatic%20standoff%2C%C2%A0Jaishankar%20confirmed%20that%20the%20issue%20came%20up%20during%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fjaishankar-blinken-canada-india-usa%5C%22%3Etalks%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20US%20secretary%20of%20state%20Anthony%20Blinken.%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20did.%E2%80%9D%20The%20US%20side%20shared%20its%20assessments%20on%20this%20whole%20situation%20and%20he%20explained%20to%20the%20Americans%20a%20summary%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20concerns%2C%20he%20noted.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20hopefully%20we%20both%20came%20out%20better%20informed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696055713000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F29133605%2FFzuFHifXoAIWH-o.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-is-non-western-not-anti-western-jaishankar-calls-for-re-globalisation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20external%20affairs%20minister%20said%20India%20aims%20to%20reorder%20the%20world%20not%20with%20a%20'pull%20down%20the%20pillars'%20approach%2C%20but%20with%20a%20reformist%20mindset%20where%20India%20would%20add%20a%20non-Western%20layer%20to%20the%20existing%20world%20architecture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-is-non-western-not-anti-western-jaishankar-calls-for-re-globalisation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Shahid%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20a%20star%20kid%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696055400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3