%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fcanadas-lentil-sales-india-slow-after-trudeau-raised-murder-suspicions-2023-09-26%2F%26source%3Dgmail-imap%26ust%3D1696647366000000%26usg%3DAOvVaw3skDygFJCc0_EbaGfEQPl3%5C%22%3Enews%20report%20from%20Reuters%20suggests%20that%20lentil%20imports%20from%20Canada%20have%20%E2%80%9Cslowed%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20after%20Canadian%20prime%20minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20accused%20Indian%20intelligence%20agents%20of%20assassinating%20a%20Canadian%20Sikh%20activist%20Canadian%20soil.%20This%20has%20implications%20for%20domestic%20pulse%20prices%20as%20India%20heads%20into%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndia%20and%20Canada%20have%20been%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-canada-fake-news-punjabis-visa%5C%22%3Emajor%20diplomatic%20tussle%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20Trudeau%20made%20his%20allegations%20public.%20The%20Indian%20government%20denies%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBut%20what%20does%20this%20have%20to%20do%20with%20Canadian%20lentils%20exports%20to%20India%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECanada%20apart%20from%20its%20vast%20mineral%20wealth%2C%20also%20has%20a%20booming%20agri%20economy.%20With%20surplus%20of%20everything%20from%20edible%20oils%20to%20lentils%20to%20feed%20cakes%2C%20Canada%20has%20been%20the%20top%20supplier%20of%20masroor%20lentils%2C%20white%2Fyellow%20pea%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20Canadian%20imports%2C%20notably%2C%20came%20in%20handy%20in%20fighting%20the%20arhar%20dal%20crisis.%20They%20have%2C%20many%20times%2C%20helped%20stabilise%20the%20prices%20and%20also%20provided%20for%20a%20major%20source%20of%20vegetarian%20protein.%20Similarly%2C%20when%20chickpea%20prices%20are%20rising%20due%20to%20short%20supply%2C%20Canadian%20white%2Fyellow%20peas%20were%20imported.%20Chickpea%20was%20also%20given%20as%20part%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20food%20rations%20relief%20which%20continued%20until%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOverall%20Canada%20lentil%20imports%20are%20vital%20for%20Indian%20nutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECanola%20oil%20and%20feed%20cake%20both%20help%20in%20the%20shortage%20of%20edible%20oil%20supply%2C%20and%20poultry%20and%20cattle%20feed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESo%20if%20we%20look%20at%20the%20entire%20agri-import%20scenario%20it%20is%20fair%20to%20conclude%20that%20Canada%20has%20a%20major%20influence%20on%20the%20lentil%20and%20edible%20oil%20security%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20especially%20true%20when%20matched%20with%20the%20Indian%20agriculture%20production%20scenario.%20For%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20including%20the%20ongoing%20Kharif%20season%2C%20rainfall%20has%20been%20erratic%2C%20causing%20major%20agrarian%20disruptions.%20Floods%20and%20droughts%20have%20plagued%20India%20in%20one%20form%20or%20the%20other.%20North%20India%20has%20reported%20a%20drought-like%20August%2C%20and%20September%20too%20is%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20dry%20in%20too%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20Lentil%20and%20oilseed%20production%20have%20both%20fallen%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fusda-india-rabi-kharif-rice-less-august-monsoon%5C%22%3EUSDA%20even%20estimates%20there%20will%20be%203%25%20drop%20in%20our%20paddy%20harvests%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20season.%20Our%20strategic%20food%20reserves%20are%20low%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENow%20with%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20trouble%20not%20ending%20soon%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20grain%20supply%20is%20stuck.%20India%20is%20already%20reporting%20low%20harvests%2C%20so%20Canada%20happens%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20few%20countries%20that%20can%20supply%20to%20the%20world.%20It%20has%20been%20watching%20the%20Indian%20food%20and%20climate%20situation%20very%20carefully.%20If%20we%20do%20not%20get%20a%20good%20Kharif%20harvest%2C%20there%20will%20be%20additional%20demand%20for%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20when%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20importance%20heightens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWith%20elections%20in%20a%20few%20months%2C%20India%20would%20need%20to%20keep%20food%20prices%20low.%20Without%20cheap%20imports%20this%20would%20be%20near%20impossible.%20Canada%20hopes%20to%20use%20lentils%20and%20other%20food%20commodities%20as%20a%20bargaining%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EExports%20and%20a%20trump%20card%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBut%20the%20agri-power%20display%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20end%20here.%20India%E2%80%99s%20agri%20exports%20to%20Canada%20could%20be%20next.%20Canada%20may%20have%20already%20started%20a%20process%20of%20limiting%20or%20putting%20extra%20scrutiny%20on%20Indian%20food%20exports.%20Ideally%20for%20Canadians%2C%20they%20want%20to%20put%20tariffs%20on%20and%20curtail%20Indian%20imports.%20No%20doubt%20India%20will%20try%20to%20reciprocate%2C%20but%20India%20may%20be%20harming%20herself%20more%20by%20banning%20or%20curtailing%20Canadian%20food%C2%A0%20imports.%20Victims%20of%20these%20decisions%20will%20be%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20still%20a%20trump%20card%20Canada%20is%20hiding%20under%20its%20sleeves.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20very%20important%20industrial%20agricultural%20fertiliser%20Muriate%20of%20Potash%20(MOP).%20Canada%20has%20the%20world%20biggest%20reserves%20of%20potash%2C%20about%2030%25.%20They%20are%20also%20the%20top%20producers%20of%20the%20fertiliser.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECanada%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20top%20exporter%20for%20MOP%2C%20apart%20from%20Russia%2C%20Belarus%2C%20etc.%20Given%20that%20agri-chemical%20fertiliser%20prices%20have%20been%20sky%20rocketing%2C%20with%20Di-ammonium%20Phosphate%20or%20DAP%20reporting%20a%2025%25%20jump.%20India%20has%20only%20a%20few%20options%20left%20to%20get%20cheap%20MOP%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20Indian%20officials%20and%20Indian%20Potash%20Limited%20have%20been%20keen%20to%20ensure%20that%20Canada%20not%20stop%20the%20potash%20shipments.%20This%20is%20simply%20because%20Indian%20food%20security%20depends%20on%20it.%20Should%20Canada%20stop%20sending%20potash%2C%20it%20will%20be%20disastrous%20for%20Rabi%20sowing%20and%20harvests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWith%20Canada%20initiating%20the%20first%20agri%20attack%2C%20India%20policymakers%20should%20quickly%20take%20stock%20of%20lentils%20and%20other%20essential%20supplies%20%E2%80%93%20a%20step%20which%20the%20government%20is%20already%20taking%20by%20imposing%20stocking%20limits%2C%20banning%20exports%20and%20strictly%20asking%20processors%20and%20retails%20to%20declare%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIf%20India%20gets%20a%20worse%20Rabi%202023-24%20wheat%20harvest%2C%20it%20may%20be%20looking%20at%20Canadian%20wheat%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIf%20this%20row%20escalates%2C%20food%20will%20potentially%20be%20used%20as%20choke%20point.%20India%20should%20focus%20on%20building%20more%20stocks%20at%20home%20or%20enter%20into%20bilateral%20agreements%20for%20food%2C%20before%20the%20granaries%20run%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%20is%20an%20independent%20agri-policy%20analyst%20and%20writer.%20He%20was%20the%20former%20director%2C%20policy%20and%20outreach%2C%20at%20NSAI.%20He%20also%20hosts%20The%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20talk%20show%2C%20Krishi%20ki%20baat%2FFarm%20Talks.%20He%20tweets%20%40indrassingh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696053889000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F17160429%2F21778186246_c5b51e6019_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Flentil-india-canada-impor