Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20on%20Saturday%20was%20hours%20from%20shutting%20down%20after%20the%20far%20right%20of%20the%20Republican%20Party%20scuppered%20final%20attempts%20at%20a%20temporary%20budget%20agreement%2C%20throwing%20into%20doubt%20everything%20from%20access%20to%20national%20parks%20to%20Washington's%20massive%20support%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20closure%20of%20all%20but%20critical%20government%20services%2C%20set%20to%20start%20after%20midnight%20Saturday%20(0400%20GMT%20Sunday)%20if%20lawmakers%20fail%20to%20reach%20a%20deal%2C%20would%20be%20the%20first%20since%202019%20--%20immediately%20delaying%20salaries%20for%20millions%20of%20federal%20employees%20and%20military%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20chambers%20of%20Congress%20are%20deadlocked%2C%20with%20a%20small%20group%20of%20Republicans%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20pushing%20back%20against%20stopgap%20measures%20that%20would%20at%20least%20keep%20the%20lights%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20House%20Republicans%20defeated%20a%20plan%20proposed%20by%20their%20own%20leader%2C%20Speaker%20Kevin%20McCarthy%2C%20to%20keep%20funds%20flowing%2C%20deepening%20the%20sense%20of%20growing%20chaos%20within%20the%20party%20ahead%20of%202024%20elections%20where%20hard-right%20former%20president%20Donald%20Trump%20hopes%20to%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-happens-if-us-government-enters-a-shutdown-4437367%5C%22%3EWhat%20Happens%20If%20US%20Government%20Enters%20A%20Shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget's%20director%20Shalanda%20Young%20said%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Bstill%20a%20chance%26quot%3B%20of%20avoiding%20a%20shutdown%20if%20Republicans%20could%20end%20internal%20divisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20White%20House%20Press%20Secretary%20Karine%20Jean-Pierre%2