%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20used%20to%20host%20a%20debate%20at%20college%2C%20and%20the%20welcome%20accorded%20to%20teams%20from%20Pakistani%20colleges%20was%20less%20loud%2C%20but%20certainly%20equally%20warm.%20There%20would%20be%20no%20dearth%20of%20volunteers%20to%20wake%20them%20up%20and%20make%20sure%20they%20got%20to%20their%20debates%20on%20time%20and%20the%20flower%20stall%20at%20the%20accompanying%20fest%20was%20always%20inundated%20with%20requests%20to%20send%20them%20flowers.%20Years%20later%2C%20I%20heard%20that%20one%20of%20the%20kids%20many%20of%20us%20made%20friends%20with%20at%20the%20debate%2C%20a%20boy%20named%20Bilal%2C%20died%20shielding%20his%20little%20nephew%20in%20a%20terrorist%20attack%20at%20a%20mosque%20in%20Karachi.%20Which%20meant%20that%20the%20first%20victim%20of%20a%20Pakistani%20terrorist%20attack%20that%20I%20had%20met%20was%20Pakistani.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20statistics%20bear%20this%20out.%20Guruswamy%20may%20be%20right%20to%20call%20out%20Pakistan%20for%20harbouring%20terrorist%20groups%20but%20in%20her%20rush%20to%20vent%20her%20ire%20on%20the%20cricket%20team%2C%20she%20forgets%20this%20%E2%80%93%20Pakistani%20civilians%20are%20among%20the%20biggest%20victims%20of%20this%20terror%20and%20by%20rabble%20rousing%20in%20India%20against%20them%2C%20we%20do%20little%20to%20help%20our%20own%20cause.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20easy%20to%20appropriate%20grief%20and%20self-righteously%20call%20for%20boycotts%20of%20cricket%20teams%20and%20artists%2C%20but%20harder%20to%20ask%20for%20accountability%20from%20our%20own%20systems%20and%20processes.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20February%202021%20%3Cem%3EFrontline%3C%2Fem%3E%20investigative%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fcover-story%2Fpulwama-attack-intelligence-inputs-ignored-national-security-leak-compromise-balakot-bjp-win-2019%2Farticle64755942.ece%5C%22%3E%3Csp