ld%20argue%20that%20true%20patriotism%20in%20the%20face%20of%20grief%20requires%20affixing%20institutional%20accountability%20within%20our%20country%20so%20that%20losses%20are%20never%20repeated%20and%20calmly%20advocating%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20our%20nation%20abroad.%20The%20petty%20thrill%20of%20finding%20personal%20targets%20to%20hate%20like%20Pakistani%20cricketers%20or%20film%20stars%20forces%20us%20to%20look%20away%20from%20the%20larger%20picture%2C%20and%20gains%20nothing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESarayu%20Pani%20is%20a%20former%20lawyer%2C%20writes%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftattva.substack.com%2F%5C%22%3Etattva.substack.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20tweets%20%40sarayupani.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696052103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F30110346%2FScreenshot-2023-09-30-at-10.50.17-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-pakistan-world-cup-cricket%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20don't%20address%20serious%20geopolitical%20issues%20and%20focus%20instead%20on%20petty%20actions%20like%20banning%20Pakistani%20artists%20from%20Bollywood%20and%20demanding%20our%20cricketers%20and%20cricket%20fans%20be%20discourteous%20to%20theirs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-pakistan-world-cup-cricket%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Varun%20hails%20Jacqueline%20for%20breaking%20boundaries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696052047000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104058752%2Cimgsize-47938.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fjacqueline-fernandez-hints-at-team-up-with-jean-claude-van-damme-varun-dhawan-congratulates-her-for-breaking-boundaries%2Farticleshow%2F104058798.cms%22%2C%22sum