al%20reality%20headset%20was%20released%20in%202013%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20watershed%20moment%20for%20technology%20fans%20everywhere.%20The%20then-cutting-edge%20Oculus%20Rift%20DK1%20was%20not%20the%20first%20VR%20headset%20ever%20created%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20first%20high-quality%20yet%20affordable%20VR%20system%20available%20to%20the%20general%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-john-carmack%5C%22%3EJohn%20Carmack%3C%2Fa%3E%20served%20as%20consulting%20chief%20technology%20officer%20for%20Meta's%20virtual%20reality%20initiatives%20since%202019%20when%20he%20transitioned%20from%20a%20full-time%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bconsulting%26quot%3B%20role.%20He%20initially%20joined%20VR%20headset%20creator%20Oculus%20in%202013%2C%20and%20the%20company%20was%20acquired%20by%20Facebook%2C%20now%20known%20as%20Meta%2C%20in%202014.%20Meta%20later%20changed%20the%20name%20of%20the%20VR%20headset%20brand%20to%20Meta%20Quest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-virtual-reality%5C%22%3EMeta%20VR%3C%2Fa%3E%20products%20currently%20include%20two%20headsets%2C%20the%20Quest%202%20and%20the%20Quest%20Pro.%20In%20June%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20it%20will%20release%20the%20Quest%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-quest-pro%5C%22%3EMeta%20Quest%20Pro%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20Meta's%20latest%20VR%20headset%20and%20has%20features%20aimed%20at%20professional%20customers%20rather%20than%20gamers%20and%20hobbyists.%20The%20Quest%20Pro%20has%20augmented%20reality%20capabilities%20integrating%20virtual%20elements%20into%20the%20real%20world.%20That%20makes%20this%20a%20so-called%20mixed-reality%20headset.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20VR%20maker%20had%20also%20sold%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-reset-oculus-go%5C%22%3EOculus%20Go%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20now