20consulates%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Hyderabad%20had%20also%20taken%20part%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FHafizZiaAhmad1%2Fstatus%2F1676168696195153920%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Emeetings%20chaired%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Taliban%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Amir%20Khan%20Muttaqi%2C%20unlike%20their%20colleagues%20in%20New%20Delhi%20who%20ignored%20any%20instructions%20from%20Kabul.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20two%20consulates%20issued%20a%20joint%20notice%20on%20their%20Facebook%20page%20on%20Friday%20rejecting%20%E2%80%9Crumours%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20consulates%20would%20be%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252FAfghanistanInMumbai%252Fposts%252Fpfbid027KdMk9YjzDeriqx4UbYndYAz1peRHNundAA5JJnznip5zDeS2cAvA1cLAJqdh8Uxl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22523%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20always%20been%20in%20close%20contact%20with%20the%20Indian%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%2C%20and%20we%20are%20grateful%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20and%20people%20who%20have%20always%20remained%20committed%20to%20their%20strategic%20partnership%20with%20Afghans%20and%20in%20the%20ongoing%20time%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Afghanistan%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20notice%20from%20the%20two%20consulates.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Afghan%20Consul%20General%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Sayed%20Mohammad%20Ibrahimkhil%2C%20said%20that%20the%20consulates%20were%20open%20and%20functional.%20He%20indicated%20that%20the%20letter%20did%20not%20have%20the%20requisite%20authority%20and%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20understand%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20the%20consulate%20had%20the%20financial%20means%20to%20remain%20open%2C%20he%20said%20that