20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Freward-asks-opposition-as-ramesh-bidhuri-gets-poll-duty-in-sachinpilots-tonk-amid-row-101695860289465.html%5C%22%3Eappointed%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20as%20its%20in-charge%20for%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Tonk%20assembly%20seat.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20relishing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBidhuri%20gained%20notoriety%20recently%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhat-it-means-indian-muslim-today%5C%22%3Ehurling%20a%20torrent%20of%20abuses%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20a%20fellow%20member%20of%20parliament%2C%20Kunwar%20Danish%20Ali%2C%20targeting%20his%20Muslim%20identity%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20parliament.%20After%20the%20initial%20outrage%20in%20the%20non-BJP%20world%2C%20the%20party%20issued%20a%20show-cause%20notice%20to%20him.%20A%20section%20of%20the%20media%20pleaded%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20draw%20a%20red%20line%20that%20must%20not%20be%20crossed%2C%20even%20if%20you%20have%20a%20heart%20filled%20with%20anti-Muslim%20venom.%20People%20lamented%20that%20the%20ever-talkative%20and%20reactive%20Narendra%20Modi%20chose%20not%20to%20utter%20a%20word!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20sought%20to%20justify%20and%20rationalise%20his%20abuses%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fdanish-ali-provoked-bidhuri-by-unpardonable-words-against-pm-nishikant-dubey-101695485880632.html%5C%22%3Eaccusing%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ali%20of%20provoking%20him%20first.%20It%20was%20using%20its%20time-tested%20%E2%80%98action-reaction%E2%80%99%20theory%20to%20justify%20its%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20making%20the%20same%20abusive%20MP%20the%20party%20in%20charge%20of%20a%20constituency%20like%20Tonk%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20sent%20a%20clear%20signal%20to%20its%20supporters%2C%20which%20include%20mainly%20Hindus%2C%20and%20Muslims%20as%20well.%20Tonk%20has%20a%20substantial%20Muslim%20population%2C%20with%20more%20than%2047%25%20of%20its%20population%20following%20Islam.%20Hindus%20make%20up%2050%25%20of%20its%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20appointing%20Bidhuri%20as%20the%20poll%20in-charge%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20sending%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20care%20about%20the%20feelings%20and%20sentiments%20of%20Muslims.%20That%20it%20does%20not%20want%20their%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20keeps%20reminding%20us%20again%20and%20again%20that%20for%20the%20party%2C%20majority%20means%20majoritarian%2C%20which%20suggests%20that%20its%20voter%20base%20will%20have%20Hindus%20and%20that%20there%20is%20no%20equal%20space%20for%20non-Hindus%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAny%20party%20would%20typically%20aim%20to%20build%20a%20majority%20by%20attracting%20all%20sections%20of%20the%20society%20to%20its%20fold.%20This%20would%20make%20the%20majority%20it%20mobilises%20a%20true%20representative%20of%20the%20people.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20follow%20this%20strategy.%20It%20has%20been%20consistently%20signalling%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9CMuslim-hater%E2%80%9D%20party.%20Nothing%20else%20explains%20otherwise%20the%20appointment%20of%20Bidhuri%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20in-charge%20in%20a%20constituency%20where%20Muslims%20are%20in%20decisive%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20outburst%20of%20Bidhuri%20was%20so%20spontaneous%2C%20the%20abuses%20flowed%20so%20effortlessly%20that%20one%20could%20realise%20that%20this%20anti-Muslim%20hatred%20is%20a%20part%20of%20his%20nature%2C%20like%20other%20BJP%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20an%20act%20also%20humiliates%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20The%20party%20is%20telling%20them%20that%20it%20has%20no%20intent%20of%20amending%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20has%20said%20it%20before%20and%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20said%20again%20that%20the%20capacity%20to%20spread%20anti-Muslim%20hatred%20is%20the%20primary%20qualification%20needed%20in%20the%20BJP%20to%20gain%20a%20seat%20and%20rise.%20That%20is%20why%20all%20leaders%2C%20even%20those%20who%20have%20spent%20their%20political%20life%20in%20a%20civilised%20political%20milieu%2C%20start%20competing%20with%20each%20other%20in%20abusing%20and%20humiliating%20Muslims%20once%20they%20are%20in%20the%20BJP.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhimanta-biswa-sarma-vegetable-price-rise-miya-muslim-market%5C%22%3EHimanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20glaring%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBidhuri%E2%80%99s%20appointment%20also%20sends%20a%20message%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20voters%3A%20that%20this%20is%20what%20we%20are.%20You%20have%20to%20accept%20us%20with%20our%20uncouthness%2C%20obscenity%2C%20and%20perversity.%20You%20did%20it%20when%20you%20elected%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmodi-discrimination-muslims-question-inequality%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Flaw-takes-whose-course-yogi-adityanath-citizenship-act-bjp-6240053%2F%5C%22%3EYogi%20Adityanath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgiriraj-singh-muslims-should-have-been-sent-to-pakistan-in-1947-2183396%5C%22%3EGiriraj%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fanurag-thakur-delhi-chants%5C%22%3EAnurag%20Thakur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fconstitutional-conduct-group-pragya-thakur-hate-speech%5C%22%3EPragya%20Thakur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fvhp-leader-sadhvi-prachi-links-mosques-and-madrasas-to-love-jihad-in-provocative-remarks%2Farticle66958200.ece%5C%22%3ESadhvi%20Prachi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20others.%20You%20should%20not%20expect%20us%20to%20be%20civilised%20and%20a%20hate%20spreader%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20am%20writing%20is%20a%20repet