new%20the%20advantages%20of%20%3Cem%3Echinar%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20is%20why%20they%20planted%20this%20tree%20in%20almost%20every%20village%20of%20Kashmir.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20is%20like%20a%20religious%20duty%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F184821%2Fkashmir-guide-saves-tourist-drowning-rouf-ahmad-dar-hero-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20will%20continue%20this%20mission%20till%20my%20last%20breath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhan%2C%20who%20still%20works%20as%20a%20daily%20wager%20to%20eke%20out%20his%20living%2C%20has%20dedicated%20two%20days%20a%20week%20to%20nurturing%20these%20trees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20climate%20is%20very%20hot%2C%20these%20%3Cem%3Echinars%20%3C%2Fem%3Erequire%20to%20be%20watered%20periodically.%20So%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20work%20for%20two%20days%20a%20week%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20I%20spend%20my%20entire%20day%20watering%20them.%20Though%20I%20am%20poor%20and%20work%20as%20a%20labourer%2C%20I%20nurture%20these%20trees%20like%20my%20own%20kids%3B%20they%20are%20like%20my%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhan%20has%20not%20married%20and%20lives%20with%20his%20mother%20and%20brothers.%20He%20has%20inspired%20his%20family%20and%20others%20to%20look%20after%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Khan%20has%20now%20extended%20his%20mission%20by%20planting%20%3Cem%3Edeodar%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20other%20pine%20trees%20in%20the%20forests.%20He%20can%20expertly%20handle%20this%20task%20now%20after%20updating%20himself%20about%20it.%20He%20continues%20to%20work%20in%20plantation%20drives%20and%20hopes%20that%20others%20will%20recognise%20the%20need%20for%20immediate%20afforestation%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20many%20aren%E2%80%99t%20much%20interested%20in%20this%20type%20of%20social%20work%20in%20my%20area%2C%20there%20are%20still%20some%20who%20visit%20and%20help%20me%20out.%20I%20hope%20someday%2C%20everyone%20realises%20the%20need%20for%20a%20green%20and%20clean%20environment%20and%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F124279%2Fpics-first-snows-transform-kashmir-mystical-wonderland-look%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMother%20Nature%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20conserved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAuthored%20by%20Firdous%20Hassan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695994405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331243%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20daily%20wager%20turned%20'Father%20of%20Chinars'%2C%20Abdul%20Ahad%20Khan's%20mission%20to%20protect%20Kashmir%20Valley's%20iconic%20tree%20started%20in%20Hatmullah%2015%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331243%2Fdaily-wager-is-father-of-chinars-kashmir-valley-environment-real-hero%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Thakur'%20Poem%3A%20Is%20BJP's%20Attack%20on%20Manoj%20Jha%20a%20Ploy%20to%20Deflect%20Attention%20from%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29183927%2FThe-Wire-23.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatna%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ERaghavendra%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%C2%A0Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(BJP%E2%80%99s)%20MLA%20from%20Bihar%2C%20has%20threatened%20to%20behead%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20leader%2C%20Manoj%20Jha%2C%20following%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20a%20poem%20in%20his%20parliament%20speech%20which%20is%20critical%20of%20feudal%20mindset.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20%5BManoj%20Jha%5D%20are%20a%20Brahmin.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20forget%20it.%20You%20have%20forgotten%20that%20I%20am%20also%20a%20Rajput.%20We%20will%20not%20even%20think%20for%20a%20second%20before%20beheading%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singh%20in%20a%20video%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20RJD%20chief%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20came%20to%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20defence%2C%20warning%20those%20making%20statements%20against%20him.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20opposing%20Jha%20for%20his%20innocuous%20quote%20should%20stay%20within%20their%20limits.%20Manoj%20Jha%20is%20an%20intellectual%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Yadav.%20Jha%20is%20a%20professor%20of%20social%20work%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20recently%20passed%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%2C%20Jha%20quoted%20from%20Hindi%20litterateur%20Omprakash%20Valmiki%E2%80%99s%20poem%2C%20which%20opens%20with%20the%20following%20lines%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKuan%20Thakur%20ka%2C%20Paani%20Thakur%20kaa%2C%20Khet%20Khalihar%20Thakur%20ka%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20well%20belongs%20to%20Thakur%3B%20so%20do%20the%20water%20and%20all%20the%20farm%20fields)%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20The%20poem%20makes%20an%20appeal%20to%20%E2%80%9Ckill%20the%20Thakur%20within%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EValmiki%20uses%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98Thakur%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20poem%20symbolically%2C%20both%20to%20depict%20the%20prevailing%20feudal%20mindset%20of%20his%20time%20as%20well%20as%20to%20call%20upon%20people%20to%20fight%20oppression%20being%20perpetuated%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste.%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20the%20poem%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20during%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20%E2%80%93%20was%20to%20call%20upon%20those%20wielding%20power%20and%20authority%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20that%20%E2%80%9Cexploitative%20Thakur%E2%80%9D%20from%20their%20psyche%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20denial%20of%20equal%20opportunities%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJha%E2%80%99s%20comments%20have%20set%20off%20a%20barrage%20of%20criticism%20from%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Thakur%20community%20across%20party%20lines%2C%20with%20BJP%20leaders%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20launching%20the%20attack%20on%20Jha.%20Several%20BJP%20leaders%20described%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20comments%20as%20%E2%80%9Canti-Rajput%E2%80%9D.%20Senior%20BJP%20leader%20from%20Bihar%2C%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%2C%20directed%20his%20criticism%20at%20the%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%2C%20asking%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20to%20apologise%20for%20his%20party%20colleague%E2%80%99s%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Row%20over%20Manoj%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20comments%20to%20divert%20attention%20from%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20BJP%2C%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20have%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it%20is%20troubled%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-danish-ali-lok-sabha-hate-speech%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Bidhuri%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98s%20episode.%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20communal%20slurs%20at%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%E2%80%99s%20MP%2C%20Danish%20Ali%2C%20in%20the%20parliament%20have%20once%20presented%20to%20the%20world%20the%20hate%20factory%20being%20run%20by%20the%20Hindutva%20brigade%2C%20with%20the%20tacit%20support%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government.%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20RJD%20and%20JD%20(U)%20believe%2C%20will%20be%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20deflect%20the%20public%20attention%20from%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20comments%20and%20train%20its%20guns%20at%20the%20opposition%2C%20given%20that%20Jha%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20RJD%2C%20is%20a%20constituent%20member%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F