0RJD%2C%20which%20is%20in%20government%20in%20Bihar%20with%20its%20alliance%20partner%20JD(U)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20Lalu%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20intervening%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20defending%20Manoj%20Jha%2C%20the%20RJD%20and%20JDU%20leaders%20belonging%20to%20the%20Rajput%20community%20will%20read%20between%20the%20lines%20now%20and%20understand%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20game%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20senior%20RJD%20leader.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20opposition%20leaders%20should%20be%20cautious%20with%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20mastered%20the%20art%20of%20diverting%20attention%20from%20its%20failure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-has-exposed-the-real-face-of-the-bjp-beyond-pr-charm-offensives-studied-silences%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Bidhuri%20Has%20Exposed%20the%20Real%20Face%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Beyond%20PR%20Charm%20Offensives%2C%20Studied%20Silences%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20some%20RJD%20and%20JD(U)%20leaders%20have%20also%20lashed%20out%20at%20Jha.%20Chetan%20Anand%2C%20RJD%20MLA%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20people%2C%20where%20he%20lives%2C%20get%20to%20hear%20this%20(poem)%2C%20they%20will%20not%20let%20him%20come%20there%E2%80%A6.%20I%20am%20shocked%20that%20people%20there%20(Rajya%20Sabha)%20listened%20to%20it.%20I%20would%20have%20protested%20then%20and%20there%20had%20I%20been%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chetan%20said.%20Chetan%20is%20the%20son%20of%20strongman%20Anand%20Mohan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20released%20from%20jail%20after%20serving%20a%20prison%20term%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20an%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20in%20the%201990s.%20Anand%20Mohan%20also%20hit%20out%20at%20Jha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Singh%2C%20JD(U)%20leader%20and%20MLC%2C%20also%20criticised%20Jha.%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20statements%20create%20division%20in%20the%20society.%20We%20are%20with%20Nitish%20Kumar%20who%20unites%20people%20from%20all%20religions%20and%20castes.%20Manoj%20Jha%20will%20get%20a%20befitting%20reply%20for%20this.%20This%20is%20an%20indecent%20statement.%20He%20should%20apologise%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20the%20Rajput%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98BJP%E2%80%99s%20trap%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20criticism%20that%20young%20leaders%20from%20RJD%20and%20JD(U)%20are%20falling%20into%20%E2%80%9CBJP%E2%80%99s%20trap%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20issue%20while%20also%20reflecting%20their%20lack%20of%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201931%2C%20Munshi%20Premchand%20wrote%20a%20short%20story%20titled%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EThakur%20ka%20Kuan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20Through%20the%20characters%20of%20Gangi%20and%20her%20ailing%20husband%20Jokhu%20%E2%80%93%20the%20couple%20hailing%20from%20the%20untouchable%20community%20%E2%80%93%20the%20great%20storyteller%20commented%20on%20the%20stranglehold%20of%20a%20feudal%20lord%20on%20the%20means%20of%20livelihood%20in%20a%20village.%20Gangi%20is%20unable%20to%20draw%20water%20from%20a%20well%20belonging%20to%20a%20Thakur%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20ailing%20for%20long%2C%20is%20compelled%20to%20drink%20contaminated%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOmprakash%20Valmiki%E2%80%99s%20poem%2C%20%E2%80%98Thakur%20ka%20Kuan%E2%80%99%20can%20be%20said%20to%20be%20a%20follow-up%20on%20Premchand%E2%80%99s%20story%20on%20the%20exploitation%20of%20the%20Dalit%20communities%20and%20disproportionate%20control%20of%20the%20feudal%20classes%20on%20the%20means%20of%20livelihood%20in%20the%20rural%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20criticism%20that%20the%20current%20crop%20of%20RJD%20and%20JD(U)%20leaders%20lack%20the%20understanding%20that%20the%20second-generation%20socialist%20leaders%2C%20including%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%2C%20and%20Shivanand%20Tiwary%2C%20possess.%20Nitish%20was%20known%20for%20his%20reading%20habit%20when%20he%20was%20a%20student%20leader.%20He%20is%20said%20to%20have%20read%20the%20complete%20writings%20of%20socialist%20icons%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%2C%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Lalu%20Yadav%20was%20not%20very%20studious%2C%20he%20gained%20an%20immense%20understanding%20of%20society%20as%20he%20was%20under%20the%20tutelage%20of%20Lohia%2C%20Narayan%2C%20Karpoori%20Thakuri%2C%20and%20others.%20He%20also%20took%20an%20active%20part%20in%20the%20movements%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20meant%20to%20free%20deprived%20sections%20from%20oppression.%20Lalu%20began%20his%20political%20career%20by%20taking%20part%20in%20the%20procession%20led%20by%20Shivanand%20Tiwary%20against%20Shankaracharya%E2%80%99s%20attack%20on%20the%20Dalits%20in%20the%20late%201960s.%20Tiwary%20is%20known%20to%20read%20and%20write%20regularly%20till%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Lalu%20defended%20Jha%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20launching%20the%20book%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESansad%20se%20Sadak%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20authored%20by%20Shivanand%20Tiwary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695994229000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F29183927%2FThe-Wire-23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthakur-poem-is-bjps-attack-on-manoj-jha-a-ploy-to-deflect-attention-from-ramesh-bidhuri%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20RJD%20MP's%20use%20of%20'Thakur%20ka%20Kuan'%20poem%20in%20his%20parliament%20speech%20has%20resulted%20in%20a%20barrage%20of%20criticism%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20described%20his%20comments%20as%20'anti-Rajput'.%20A%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Bihar%20has%20threatened%20to%20behead%20Jha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22