ollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investindia.gov.in%2Fsector%2Fleather%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ea%20Government%20of%20India%20website%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20leather%20industry%20in%20India%20accounts%20for%20around%2013%25%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20leather%20production%20of%20hides%2Fskins%20and%20handles%20robust%20annual%20production%20of%20about%20three%20billion%20square%20feet%20of%20leather.%E2%80%9D%20When%20employed%20in%20the%20textile%2C%20garment%20and%20footwear%20industry%2C%20however%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20scrap%20leather%20is%20generated%20during%20the%20production%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fashion%20industry%2C%20Ribhav%20notes%20that%20wastage%20exists%20at%20each%20stage%20from%20product%20designing%20to%20development%20and%20scaled%20production.%20Huge%20proportions%20of%20waste%20are%20generated%20to%20maximise%20profits%2C%20particularly%20during%20scaled%20production%2C%20to%20save%20time%20and%20costs%20per%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20leather%20is%20infamous%20for%20being%20bad%20for%20the%20environment.%20But%20what%20about%20scrap%20that%20is%20already%20present%20and%20available%3F%20My%20vision%20was%20to%20use%20this%20waste%20leather%20to%20make%20luxury%20products%2C%20and%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20brainstorming%2C%20we%20came%20up%20with%20our%20first%20collection%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.econock.com%2Fpages%2Fsophisticated-survivor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESophisticated%20Survivor%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20marked%20the%20start%20of%20Econock%E2%80%99s%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ribhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20source%20material%20Econock%20employs%20is%20leather%20scraps%20which%20are%20oddly%20shaped%20and%20sized.%20They%20are%20mostly%20remains%20and%20cut-outs%20of%20larger%20leather%20skins.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20the%20example%20of%20the%20Nora%20Tote%20Bag%20from%20our%20Sophisticated%20Survivor%20collection.%20The%20base%20is%20made%20out%20of%20waste%20leather.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20two%20halves%20on%20the%20surface%20are%20created%20from%20a%20single%20sheet%20of%20leather%20with%20the%20positive%20part%20placed%20on%20the%20upper%20panel%20and%20the%20remaining%20waste%20utilised%20in%20the%20bottom%20sections%20so%20that%20there%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F263620%2Ffarmse-farms-on-wheels-organic-zero-waste-store-ahmedabad-organic-success%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ezero%20wastage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Ribhav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20the%20fashion%20industry%20needs%20to%20be%20mindful%20while%20creating%20new%20products%20and%20designs%20and%20be%20conscious%20of%20the%20wastage%20that%20is%20generated.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20world%20where%20high%20fashion%20is%20synonymous%20with%20sustainability%2C%20where%20each%20piece%20is%20thoughtfully%20crafted%20to%20minimise%20waste%20and%20be%20environmentally%20conscious%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-2-1695911227.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22high%20luxury%20fashion%20made%20of%20waste%20leather%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-2-1695911227.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-2-1695911227-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-2-1695911227-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-2-1695911227-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Product-2-1695911227-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENora%20Tote%20Bag%20(left)%20and%20Urumi%20Clutch%20(right)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Gouri%20Rawat%2C%20the%20creative%20head%20at%20Econock%2C%20talks%20about%20the%20choice%20of%20working%20with%20scrap%20leather%20and%20why%20their%20brand%20went%20ahead%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20first%20worked%20with%20scrap%20leather%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20people%20questioned%20our%20choice%20of%20material.%20They%20asked%20us%20why%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20use%20more%20vegan%20materials.%20We%20do%20not%20endorse%20the%20use%20of%20leather%20but%20scraps%20(waste)%20exist.%20Even%20with%20new-age%20materials%20like%20cork%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20overlook%20the%20aspect%20of%20scraps%20being%20present%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20harming%20the%20environment%20as%20well.%20Our%20work%20is%20to%20upcycle%20these%20scrap%20materials%20and%20eradicate%20waste%20that%20ends%20up%20in%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Gouri.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20goes%20on%20to%20add%2C%20%E2%80%9CWith%20scrap%20leather%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20started%20reinventing%20surface%20embellishments%20and%20techniques%20to%20find%20ways%20of%20upcycling%20this%20waste.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-and-Gouri-1695910018.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Making%20luxury%20fashion%20out%20of%20waste%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-and-Gouri-1695910018.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-and-Gouri-1695910018-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-and-Gouri-1695910018-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-and-Gouri-1695910018-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Ribhav-and-Gouri-1695910018-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331203%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECreative%20Brains%20Behind%20Econock%3A%20Ribhav%20Kapur%20and%20Gouri%20Rawat%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20all%20scrap%20leather%20is%20the%20same%2C%20and%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20they%E2%80%99re%20a%20luxury%20brand%2C%20a%20certain%20degree%20of%20quality%20is%20expected.%20To%20ensure%20quality%2C%20Ribhav%20notes%20that%20Econock%20sources%20scrap%20leather%20from%20renowned%20leather%20traders%20for%20export%20and%20industry%20suppliers%20in%20Paharganj%20and%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20built%20mutually%20beneficial%20relationships%20wherein%20we%20have%20monetised%20their%20discards%2C%20thereby%20establishing%20a%20reliable%20and%20sustainable%20supply%20chain.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20we%20only%20use%20leather%20scraps.%20We%20do%20not%20recycle%20old%20leather%20to%20make%20new%20products%20because%20that%20requires%20an%20extensive%20%5Bchemical%5D%20treatment%20process.%20However%2C%20we%20do%20offer%20customisation%20of%20old%20leather%20bags%20for%20our%20customers%20so%20that%20they%20can%20reuse%20them%20in%20new%20avatars%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESourcing%20scrap%20leather%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20challenge.%20The%20primary%20challenge%2C%20according%20to%20Ribhav%2C%20i