ma%20and%20his%20father%20then%20motivated%20him%20to%20start%20a%20venture%20focused%20on%20sustainability.%20Parth%20recalls%20an%20incident%20that%20their%20father%2C%20who%20frequented%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20society%20circles%2C%20narrated%20to%20them%20about%20how%20many%20affluent%20families%20discard%20shoes%20after%20barely%20using%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20just%20adds%20to%20the%20unnecessary%20pile%20of%20existing%20shoes%20in%20the%20landfills%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20got%20the%20siblings%20thinking%2C%20if%20given%20a%20choice%2C%20would%20people%20shelling%20out%20money%20for%20high-end%20shoes%20make%20a%20sustainable%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F287173%2Fneemans-sustainable-shoe-company-recycled-plastic-bottles-tyres-rubber%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmentally-conscious%20%3C%2Fa%3Epurchase%20too%2C%20if%20given%20a%20choice%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20Parth%20and%20Karishma%20decided%20to%20manufacture%20shoes%20that%20are%20sustainable%2C%20eco-friendly%2C%20and%20also%20with%20a%20high%20finish.%20These%20shoes%20can%20also%20be%20recycled%20unlike%20the%20conventional%20leather%20or%20rubber%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-3-1695904785.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parth%20and%20Karishma%20Dalal%20launched%20Reroute%20to%20redefine%20the%20footwear%20industry%20that%20has%20long%20been%20associated%20with%20excessive%20carbon%20emissions.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-3-1695904785.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FReroute-3-1695904785-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20http