f%20expanding.%20Thanks%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20Make%20in%20India%20push%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20go%20big%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramji.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Forget%20your%20age%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miniature%20models%20made%20by%20Craftizan%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FUntitled-design-2023-09-27T190445.028-1695823179-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-331084%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMiniature%20models%20made%20by%20Craftizan%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20incredible%20to%20see%20how%20Ramji%20has%20the%20energy%20of%20a%2030-year-old.%20He%E2%80%99s%20raring%20to%20go%20and%20is%20looking%20at%20a%20world%20of%20opportunities.%20He%E2%80%99s%20got%20no%20plans%20of%20retiring%20any%20time%20soon.%20His%20day%20at%20the%20factory%20starts%20at%209%20am%20and%20goes%20on%20till%207-8pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20love%20to%20work%20on%20my%20models%20with%20some%20Carnatic%20mu