%20artisan%20community%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20spent%20her%20early%20married%20life%20looking%20after%20her%20in-laws%20and%20children.%20Wanting%20to%20send%20her%20children%20to%20a%20good%20school%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20join%20her%20husband%20in%20the%20craft%20work.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20money%20coming%20into%20the%20house%20was%20not%20enough%20to%20send%20my%20children%20to%20a%20good%20school.%20However%2C%20even%20after%20the%20two%20of%20us%20started%20working%20together%2C%20we%20were%20still%20not%20able%20to%20afford%20the%20fees%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20toil%20and%20dedication%20of%20these%20artisans%20are%20often%20met%20with%20meagre%20wages.%20Swarnalata%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20wages%20can%20plummet%20as%20low%20as%20Rs%201%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20which%20is%20hardly%20enough%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%E2%80%9D%20Balancing%20household%20chores%20and%20contributing%20to%20her%20husband%E2%80%99s%20craftwork%20had%20become%20increasingly%20taxing%20for%20Swarnalata.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20something%20changed.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20introduced%20me%20to%20the%20Karya%20Project%20and%20suggested%20I%20get%20involved.%20The%20work%20is%20quite%20simple%3B%20all%20I%20have%20to%20do%20is%20speak%20in%20Odiya%20on%20my%20phone%2C%20it%20gets%20recorded%2C%20and%20then%20I%20get%20paid!%E2%80%9D%20Swarnalata%20informs%20that%20she%20was%20paid%20Rs%204%2C000%20after%20working%20for%20just%20one%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEstablished%20in%202021%20by%20Manu%20Chopra%20and%20Vivek%20Seshadri%2C%20with%20Safiya%20Husain%20joining%20a%20year%20later%2C%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20Karya%20Project%20uses%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20help%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F119176%2Fhow-rural-indians-can-get-same-opportunities-as-urban-counterparts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erural%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%20find%20respectable%20work.%20Workers%20use%20the%20%E2%80%98Karya%E2%80%99%20app%20to%20record%20audio%20in%20their%20native%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Karya%20Project%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpecialised%20AI%2C%20like%20large%20language%20models%20like%20Chat%20GPT%2C%20primarily%20uses%20English%20due%20to%20the%20abundance%20of%20text%20and%20audio%20data%20available.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20need%20for%20databases%20containing%20languages%20spoken%20in%20India%20other%20than%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20if%20Chat%20GPT%20were%20to%20operate%20in%20Kanada%2C%20the%20AI%20would%20require%20a%20substantial%20amount%20of%20audio%20and%20text%20data%20for%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Karya%20Project%20steps%20into%20this%20role%20by%20collecting%20and%20selling%20such%20data%20in%20different%20languages%20to%20its%20clients.%20However%2C%20what%20sets%20the%20project%20apart%20is%20not%20its%20novelty%20or%20uniqueness%2C%20but%20its%20nonprofit%20model.%20After%20covering%20its%20costs%2C%20the%20profits%20from%20these%20sales%20are%20channelled%20directly%20into%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20workers%2C%20Manu%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkarya-feature-1-1695819981.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20workers%20of%20Karya%20are%20paid%20instantly%20and%20can%20work%20remotely%20using%20the%20company's%20app.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkarya-feature-1-1695819981.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkarya-feature-1-1695819981-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploa