ul%20vocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20should%20have%20patience%20and%20perseverance%20to%20take%20up%20this%20task.%20One%20has%20to%20wait%20for%20two%20years%20for%20a%20suitable%20and%20proper%20yield%20at%20first.%20An%20acre%20of%20land%20may%20only%20produce%2060%2C000%20flowers%2C%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20but%20wait%20and%20watch%20in%20wonder%20how%20that%20number%20slowly%20shoots%20up%20to%20almost%20two%20lakhs%20soon.%20My%20training%20in%20the%20army%20has%20helped%20me%20immensely%20with%20this%20profession.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20only%20reason%20why%20I%20am%20now%20able%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20wife%20of%20an%20army%20man%2C%20I%20have%20been%20ingrained%20with%20these%20traits%20as%20well.%20I%20have%20to%20play%20the%20role%20of%20a%20robust%20support%20system%20both%20in%20his%20personal%20and%20professional%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Monalisa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20always%20smooth%20sailing%20for%20Sujan%20before%20he%20decided%20on%20orchid%20cultivation%2C%20a%20venture%20which%20is%20totally%20alien%20to%20him.%20But%20with%20pure%20dedication%20and%20determination%2C%20his%20idea%20took%20root%20and%20then%20there%20was%20no%20turning%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-Monalisha-with-visitors_11zon-1695306130.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mohantys%20with%20visitors%20at%20their%20farm.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-Monalisha-with-visitors_11zon-1695306130.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FCornel-Mohanty-Monalisha-with-visitors_11zon-1695306130-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20ht